content.body:
### Shop 35x10.50R17LT Tire Size 
Trucks that are equipped with lift kits (think Chevy Silverado 2500, Dodge RAM 2500, Ford F-250) need an extra measure of ground clearance, and that’s where big tires come in. The 35x10.50R17LT is a supersize tire you might find on trucks like these, with a tough all-terrain tread for aggressive traction and durability. 

All-terrain and mud terrain tires are great for drivers who need extra traction, performance, and durability when driving on- and off-road. Check out the [Kenda Klever R/T KR601](https://simpletire.com/brands/kenda-tires/klever-r-t-kr601), Fury Country Hunter A/T, and Venom Power Terra Hunter X/T if you need a set of 35x10.50R17LT tires that can reliably get you through mud, sand, snow and loose dirt and back on the highway again, with aggressive tread patterns and reinforced, damage-resistant casings.

Whether you need a mud terrain, all-terrain, or another type of tire for your lifted truck, SimpleTire has a set of 35x10.50R17LT tires that meets your needs at a great price!
